=== 日本 ===
日本宫古岛是鸣蝉袭击的第一个岛屿，当地阵风时速达266公里，持续风速也有每小时152公里。前后16小时里，除风眼经过的两小时外，岛上气压低至912毫巴（百帕，26.87英寸汞柱），是当地有纪录以来的第2低气压值，仅次于1959年的颱風莎拉，而且当时还是全日本历史上的第4低气压值<ref name="gp" />。风暴在宫古岛降下暴雨，降雨总量达470毫米，其中24小时降雨量高达402.5毫米，刷新单日雨量纪录。岛上的1小时降雨量有58.5毫米，其中仅10分钟的雨量就有22毫米。<ref name="gp" /><ref name="dt3">{{cite report |author=Digital Typhoon |publisher=National Institute of Informatics |title=Weather Disaster Report (2003-927-03) |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20131019180632/http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/report.pl?id=2003-927-03&lang=en |url=http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/report.pl?id=2003-927-03&lang=en |deadurl=no |accessdate=2016-03-16 |archivedate=2013-10-19 }}</ref>宫古岛有104幢建筑因气旋受损<ref name="dt3" />，其中两幢房屋程度严重<ref name="ap910" />。鸣蝉还令36处公路路段受损，并在岛上引起停电<ref name="dt3" />，有约2万零900人受影响，占全岛人口的95%<ref name="jen910">{{cite news | agency = Japan Economic Newswire | date = 2003-09-10 | title = Typhoon Maemi hits Miyakojima Island, 63 injured}}{{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>。此外，宫本岛还有一人被飞溅的玻璃割伤致死<ref name="ap911" />。

多家新闻机构宣称，鸣蝉是1968年后袭击冲绳的最强台风<ref name="ap911" />。[[冲绳县|冲绳县]][[名护市|名护市]]的阵风时速达到109公里<ref name="gp" />。[[石垣岛|石垣岛]]有许多房屋和农作物因狂风受损，多幢建在低洼地区的建筑被高涨的潮汐淹没<ref>{{cite report |author=Digital Typhoon |publisher=National Institute of Informatics |title=Weather Disaster Report (2003-918-10) |accessdate=2016-03-16 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20131019180632/http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/report.pl?id=2003-918-10&lang=en |archivedate=2013-10-19 |deadurl=no |url=http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/report.pl?id=2003-918-10&lang=en }}</ref>。冲绳各地共有94人受伤，其中大部分都是被破碎的玻璃割伤<ref name="ap911">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press International | author = Eric Talmadge | date = 2003-09-11 | title = Powerful typhoon sweeps across Japan's southern islands; one dead, dozens injured}}{{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>。

登陆韩国前不久，鸣蝉在位于日本和韩国之间中途海域的[[对马岛|对马岛]]产生时速167公里的阵风。位于日本西南海岸的平户市有气象站测得时速113公里的阵风。<ref name="gp" />台风在日本[[九州_(日本)|九州]]降下暴雨，[[宫崎县|宫崎县]]有气象站测得457毫米雨量<ref name="dt" />。降水在[[长崎县|长崎县]]引起[[山崩|山体滑坡]]，191人被迫撤离家园<ref>{{cite report |author=Digital Typhoon |publisher=National Institute of Informatics |title=Weather Disaster Report (2003-817-25) |accessdate=2016-03-16 |url=http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/report.pl?id=2003-817-25&lang=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20131019180620/http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/report.pl?id=2003-817-25&lang=en |archivedate=2013-10-19 }}</ref>。暴雨还在[[大分县|大分县]]和高知县引起山崩<ref>{{cite report |author=Digital Typhoon |publisher=National Institute of Informatics |title=Weather Disaster Report (2003-815-10) |accessdate=2016-03-16 |url=http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/report.pl?id=2003-815-10&lang=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20131019180633/http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/report.pl?id=2003-815-10&lang=en |archivedate=2013-10-19 }}</ref>，高知县有多条道路因此封闭<ref>{{cite report |author=Digital Typhoon |publisher=National Institute of Informatics |title=Weather Disaster Report (2003-893-13) |accessdate=2013-10-18 |url=http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/report.pl?id=2003-893-13&lang=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20131019180631/http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/report.pl?id=2003-893-13&lang=en |archivedate=2013-10-19 }}</ref>。面对台风威胁，[[山口县|山口县]]有多座学校关闭<ref>{{cite report |author=Digital Typhoon |publisher=National Institute of Informatics |title=Weather Disaster Report (2003-762-18) |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20131019180619/http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/report.pl?id=2003-762-18&lang=en |accessdate=2016-03-16 |url=http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/report.pl?id=2003-762-18&lang=en |archivedate=2013-10-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。风暴在高知县催生出一场[[藤田级数|藤田级数]]为{{lang|en|F}}1的[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]，多幢房屋因此受损，还有一辆汽车翻转，车内一名女性受伤<ref>{{cite report |author=Digital Typhoon |publisher=National Institute of Informatics |title=Weather Disaster Report (2003-893-07) |url=http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/report.pl?id=2003-893-07&lang=en |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20131019180641/http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/report.pl?id=2003-893-07&lang=en |accessdate=2016-03-16 |archivedate=2013-10-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。转变成温带风暴后，鸣蝉还给[[北海道|北海道]][[函馆市|函馆市]]带去时速约108公里的阵风，致使约2500居民失去供电<ref name="dt2">{{cite report |author=Digital Typhoon |publisher=National Institute of Informatics |title=Weather Disaster Report (2003-430-03) |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20131018165039/http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/report.pl?id=2003-430-03&lang=en |url=http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/report.pl?id=2003-430-03&lang=en |deadurl=no |accessdate=2016-03-16 |archivedate=2013-10-18 }}</ref>。[[秋田市|秋田市]]某气象站测得时速116公里的阵风，是该站历史上测得的9月第3高风速<ref name="dt4">{{cite report |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20131018165018/http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/report.pl?id=2003-582-08&lang=en |author=Digital Typhoon |publisher=National Institute of Informatics |title=Weather Disaster Report (2003-582-08) |url=http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/report.pl?id=2003-582-08&lang=en |accessdate=2013-10-18 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2013-10-18 }}</ref>。[[札幌市|札幌市]]有一人被倒塌的树木砸死，另有两人受伤<ref>{{cite report |author=Digital Typhoon |publisher=National Institute of Informatics |title=Weather Disaster Report (2003-412-04) |accessdate=2016-03-16 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20131018165046/http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/report.pl?id=2003-412-04&lang=en |url=http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/report.pl?id=2003-412-04&lang=en |archivedate=2013-10-18 }}</ref>。单[[松前町_(北海道)|松前町]]就有多个渔场和54条船只因大浪受损<ref name="dt2" />，全日本受损船只的数量则有262条<ref name="dt" />。[[秋田县|秋田县]]有一人因遭遇恶劣海况丧生<ref name="dt4" />。日本各地共有1498幢民居被风暴摧毁，另有363套被淹。气旋还导致约9公顷田地受到破坏。总体而计，日本共有3人因鸣蝉遇难，另有107人受伤，其中两人伤势严重，总体经济损失约为113亿[[日圆|日圆]]（2003年日圆，相当于同年的9600万[[美元|美元]]{{refn|报道中原本采用的货币单位是[[日圆|日圆]]，经{{lang|en|OANDA}}公司网站外汇历史汇率页面换算成美元<ref name="oanda">{{cite web | publisher = Oanda Corporation | year = 2015 | title = 历史汇率 | accessdate = 2015-03-31 | url = http://www.oanda.com/currency/historical-rates/ | archive-date = 2013-10-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131004000103/http://www.oanda.com/currency/historical-rates/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>|group="注"|name="jpy"}}）<ref name="dt">{{cite report |author=Digital Typhoon |title=Typhoon 200314 (Maemi) |accessdate=2016-03-16 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20131018152747/http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/dsummary.pl?id=200314&basin=wnp&lang=en |url=http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/dsummary.pl?id=200314&basin=wnp&lang=en |archivedate=2013-10-18 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

=== 韓國 ===
[[File:ST_Maemi_12_sep_2003_0455Z.jpg|right]]
鸣蝉吹袭韩国期间产生暴雨，最高降雨量达453毫米<ref name="gc" />。[[南海郡_(韩国)|南海郡]]和济州岛的雨量分别达401.5毫米<ref name="gp" />和255毫米<ref name="kh914" />。气旋产生的降水范围比一年前袭击韩国的[[台风鹿莎|台风鹿莎]]小，洪灾严重程度也有不及，但鸣蝉引起的风害更大<ref name="dpri">{{cite report | author1 = Sunmin Kim | author2 = Yasuto Tachikawa | author3 = Kaoru Takara | deadurl = no | title = Recent Flood Disasters and Progress of Disaster Management System in Korea | publisher = Disaster Prevention Research Institute | year = 2007 | url = http://repository.kulib.kyoto-u.ac.jp/dspace/bitstream/2433/73352/1/a50b0p02.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303230240/http://repository.kulib.kyoto-u.ac.jp/dspace/bitstream/2433/73352/1/a50b0p02.pdf | format = PDF | accessdate = 2016-03-16 | archivedate = 2016-03-03}}</ref>。济州岛测得的阵风时速达216公里，最低气压950毫巴（百帕，28英寸汞柱），两项数据都刷新该国纪录<ref name="nema" />。其中风速打破[[台风派比安_(2000年)|台风派比安]]2000年创下的每小时210公里纪录<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = Korea Times | date = 2003-09-14 | title = Maemi' Most Powerful Typhoon}}{{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>，气压则比1959年的颱風莎拉还要低1.5毫巴<ref name="nema" />，打破已保持40余年的纪录<ref name="gc" />。位于韩国本土的[[金海国际机场|金海国际机场]]测得时速143公里的阵风<ref name="gp" />。釜山的风速也达到每小时154公里，是该市有纪录以来的第二高风速，仅次于1987年的[[1987年台风塞尔玛|台风塞尔玛]]<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = Korea Times | author = Hong Seo-rim | date = 2003-09-14 | title = Typhoon Causes Blackouts, Floods}}{{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>。狂风冲击之下，韩国有[[韩国核能|5座核电站]]自动关闭，但最终都没有受到影响<ref name="kis" />。

[[庆尚南道|庆尚南道]]有71人丧生，是韩国受灾最严重的所在<ref name="jd916" />。釜山的灾情也特别重大，[[醴泉郡|醴泉]]、[[蔚山广域市|蔚山]]和[[大邱广域市|大邱]]都受到重创。釜山有11台各重约900吨的起重吊车在狂风下倒塌，<ref name="gc" />致使两人丧生，5人受伤<ref name="afp914">{{cite news | agency = Agence France-Presse | date = 2003-09-14 | title = 109 people dead or missing as South Korea counts cost of killer typhoon | publisher = ReliefWeb | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303233108/http://reliefweb.int/report/republic-korea/109-people-dead-or-missing-south-korea-counts-cost-killer-typhoon | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2013-10-24 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/republic-korea/109-people-dead-or-missing-south-korea-counts-cost-killer-typhoon}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | agency = Japan Economic Newswire | date = 2003-09-13 | title = Typhoon Maemi leaves 48 dead, 25 missing in S. Korea}}{{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>。当地有多家造船厂关闭<ref name="gc" />，初步报告估计釜山港需要一整年才能全面恢复运作<ref name="jd915">{{cite news | newspaper = JoongOng Daily | publisher = ReliefWeb | date = 2003-09-15 | accessdate = 2016-03-16 | title = Rep. of Korea: Typhoon devastates the nation's south | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304090249/http://reliefweb.int/report/republic-korea/rep-korea-typhoon-devastates-nations-south | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/republic-korea/rep-korea-typhoon-devastates-nations-south | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。估计港口所受破坏价值约有5000万美元<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = South China Morning Post | author = Russell Barling | date = 2003-09-16 | title = Typhoon costs Hutchison $ 20m}}{{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>，导致载货量下降20%之多<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | author = James Brooke | date = 2003-09-17 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2003/09/17/business/typhoon-hits-south-korea-economy.html | title = Typhoon Hits South Korea Economy | accessdate = 2016-03-16 | publisher = The New York Times Company | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150527234735/http://www.nytimes.com/2003/09/17/business/typhoon-hits-south-korea-economy.html | archivedate = 2015-05-27}}{{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>。釜山海域还有艘大型船只因巨浪侧翻，[[蔚山广域市|蔚山]]近海也有家海上造船厂被海浪推向石油设施，令其双双受损<ref name="gc" />。釜山共有16人因风暴遇难<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = Korea Times | date = 2003-09-22 | title = Special Disaster Zones to Be Declared}}{{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>。

沿海地区有数以百计的房屋被高涨的潮汐淹没，缺乏海堤保护的地点情况尤为严重<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = Korea Times | date = 2003-09-17 | title = Typhoon Deaths Blamed on Negligence}}{{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>。鸣蝉导致[[马山市|马山市]]一家地下购物中心被淹，夺走12条人命<ref name="jd916" />。[[韩国电视剧|韩国电视剧]]《[[洛城生死恋|洛城生死恋]]》正在该国西南近海的济州岛取景，但外景地被来袭的气旋摧毁<ref>{{cite news | author = Chung Ah-young | newspaper = Korea Times | date = 2007-11-01 | title = Dramatic Legacy Still Goes on Locations Nationwide | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304073251/http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/art/2008/04/203_12955.html | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2013-10-25 | url = http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/art/2008/04/203_12955.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04}}</ref>，岛上还有32套房屋被毁，另有两人遇难<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = Korea Times | date = 2003-09-14 | title = Typhoon Smashes Nation}}{{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>，其中一人当时正试图固定自己的船只<ref>{{cite news | agency = [[法新社|Agence France-Presse]] | date = 2003-09-13 | title = Typhoon Maemi kills 58 in South Korea, 27 still missing}}{{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>，韩国各地共有465艘船受损或搁浅。强降雨引发多场[[泥石流|泥石流]]，其中[[忠清道|忠清道]]有列火车因此出轨，致使28名乘客受伤<ref name="gc" />。泥石流还令多条道路封闭<ref name="ifrc915" />，有10处地点的5条铁道受到破坏<ref>{{cite news | author = Yang Sung-jin | newspaper = Korea Herald | date = 2003-09-15 | title = Typhoon hurts key industries}}{{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>。韩国各地有近4万辆汽车受损<ref name="gc" />，另有2278条道路或桥梁受到破坏<ref name="nema" />。洛东江因暴雨泛滥，釜山附近河段水位达5.06米，属洪水警戒水位。此河段河水排放量达每秒1万3000立方米，足以摧毁一截桥梁。<ref name="hyd">{{cite report | author1 = Un Ji | author2 = Pierre Julien | title = Typhoon Maemi and Impacts on Lower Nakdong River, South Korea | newspaper = Hydrology Days | year = 2005 | accessdate = 2016-03-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304085222/http://hydrologydays.colostate.edu/Papers_2005/Ji_paper.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://hydrologydays.colostate.edu/Papers_2005/Ji_paper.pdf | format = PDF | archivedate = 2016-03-04}}</ref>洛东江的支流也有类似情况，位于大邱附近的一座堤坝被洪水摧毁<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = Korea Herald | date = 2003-09-15 | title = Full-scale recovery work launched}}{{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>。台风还令3万7986公顷即将迎来秋收的农田被淹<ref name="gc" />，稻米作物因此受到大范围破坏<ref name="hyd" />。韩国东岸近海的[[郁陵岛|郁陵岛]]有许多房屋和一条主要公路被冲毁，导致3人遇难。当地居民指责政府和气象机构没有提前发布预警。<ref name="jd919">{{cite news | author = Hong Gwon-sam | date = 2003-09-19 | newspaper = JoongAng Daily | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304070841/http://reliefweb.int/report/republic-korea/rep-koreatyphoon-maemi-anger-mounts-over-lack-typhoon-warnings | publisher = ReliefWeb | title = Rep. of Korea/Typhoon Maemi: Anger mounts over lack of typhoon warnings | accessdate = 2013-10-24 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/republic-korea/rep-koreatyphoon-maemi-anger-mounts-over-lack-typhoon-warnings}}</ref>

整场台风一共导致韩国147万用户失去供电<ref name="kis">{{cite report | agency = Korean Information Service | publisher = ReliefWeb | date = 2003-09-15 | title = Rep. of Korea: Government provides funds for rescue operations in typhoon-hit areas | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/republic-korea/rep-korea-government-provides-funds-rescue-operations-typhoon-hit-areas | accessdate = 2013-10-24 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304091414/http://reliefweb.int/report/republic-korea/rep-korea-government-provides-funds-rescue-operations-typhoon-hit-areas}}</ref>，单电力公司遭受的损失总额就有129亿[[韩圆|韩圆]]（2003年韩圆，相当于同年的1161万美元{{refn|报道中原本采用的货币单位是[[韩圆|韩圆]]，经{{lang|en|OANDA}}公司网站外汇历史汇率页面换算成美元<ref name="oanda" />。|group="注"|name="won"}}）<ref name="afp914" />。受大范围破坏影响，多地的移动电话和手机服务中断<ref name="mark">{{cite news | author = Mark Bellows | newspaper = The Evening Times | location = Newcastle, United Kingdom | date = 2003-09-13 | title = 33 are killed in typhoon terror}}{{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>。美国在该国的多座[[美国驻韩军事基地|军事基地]]一共受到价值约450万美元的损失<ref>{{cite news | author1 = Franklin Fisher | author2 = Joseph Giordono | newspaper = Stars and Stripes | date = 2004-08-21 | title = S. Korea bases report minor typhoon damages | accessdate = 2016-03-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303231129/http://www.stripes.com/news/s-korea-bases-report-minor-typhoon-damages-1.23461 | url = http://www.stripes.com/news/s-korea-bases-report-minor-typhoon-damages-1.23461 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。韩国各地共有约5000套房屋被毁，1万3000户民宅或商铺受损<ref name="gc" />，致使约2万5000人无家可归<ref name="afp914" />。2002年台风鹿莎来袭期间，[[江原道_(韩国)|江原道]]就有约150家企业毁于一旦，经过重建后又被鸣蝉摧毁<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = JoongAng Daily | date = 2003-09-17 | author = Lee Chan-ho | title = Rep. of Korea: After a double blow, typhoon victims say Seoul was part of their problems | accessdate = 2016-03-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304055938/http://reliefweb.int/report/republic-korea/rep-korea-after-double-blow-typhoon-victims-say-seoul-was-part-their-problems | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/republic-korea/rep-korea-after-double-blow-typhoon-victims-say-seoul-was-part-their-problems}}</ref>。台风引起的保险索赔总额估计有6500亿韩圆（2003年韩圆，相当于同年的5亿6500万美元），其中大部分是财物损失{{refn|韩国的损失总额由佳达再保险经纪有限公司提供。|group="注"}}，相当于一年前台风鹿莎的4倍。相比之下，鸣蝉在韩国造成的损失总额估计为5万5200亿韩圆（2003年韩圆，相当于同年的48亿美元），反而比鹿莎要少2万5200亿韩圆（相当于2003年的19亿美元），这种情况的出现主要是因为鸣蝉引起的工业破坏数额较高，而鹿莎的总体破坏程度更大。<ref name="gc" />风暴在韩国各地共计夺走117人的生命<ref name="nema" />。

